{"tid":2223251,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢一刻有咩歌觸動了你個心？","createTime":"2020-09-29T16:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T20:05:25.000Z","uid":209553,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"5daa744701351ac4327509ec9f96ae1a4dc10c2a","tid":2223251,"uid":209553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"很久很久以後我們才知道，<br />\n當一個女生說她再也不理你，<br />\n不是真的討厭你，<br />\n而是她很在乎你，<br />\n非常非常在乎你。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181e76ae6179c4d66859544c8df4ba6855882463","tid":2223251,"uid":288304,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"何以..."},{"pid":"56baed358408227dbfc766034202720a8e454f39","tid":2223251,"uid":366459,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:11:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4a50b649f516ef36d59bc4fd1dff8b845b64b7b","tid":2223251,"uid":42767,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:12:58.000Z","msg":"願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"cc08638887270550b80e6b7a850eaff66c58266f","tid":2223251,"uid":127929,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:13:38.000Z","msg":"願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"24327a061bfd5970565d9062de4c7e38ec4fc6ce","tid":2223251,"uid":126896,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"當時奮不顧身伸出我的手<br />\n看見了輪廓就當作宇宙<br />\n甜美的習慣變成生活<br />\n才瞭解了什麼"},{"pid":"5acae9c75bf2efd0addf453a1f37bbd2c672cafe","tid":2223251,"uid":141951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"為你摧毀肉身　為你遭遢靈魂  <br />\n跌到了最暗處　人忽爾明瞭 <br />\n賠掉我一生　未見得使你關心 <br />\n明日我必須振作　這段情當作 從未發生 <br />\n然後每一天　活得好你一點 <br />\n來讓你今天碰見　 那日離棄我　原是你損失"},{"pid":"41f3608bb554e0fed3d9c94cdd53dde30dbaed48","tid":2223251,"uid":170375,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:15:22.000Z","msg":"一萬九索都俾對家扣起了多涼薄<br />\n這十三幺摸到盡了雀仔難尋獲<br />\n在叫糊待一索對面原來是雞糊上落<br />\